<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.3.8">
<l>muṉṉiv vēḻula kuṇarviṉṟi yiruḷmika vumparkaḷ toḻutētta</l>
<l>vaṉṉa mākiyaṉ ṟarumaṟai payantava ṉēyeṉak karuḷpuriyē</l>
<l>maṉṉu kētakai cūtaka meṉṟivai vaṉattiṭaic curumpiṉaṅkaḷ</l>
<l>teṉṉa veṉṉavaṇ ṭiṉṉicai muraltiru veḷḷaṟai niṉṟāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[Lord] who, as a swan which the celestials adored and praised,</l>
<l rend="indent">produced the rare Vedas that day</l>
<l>When, long ago, darkness intensified [until] discernment</l>
<l rend="indent">of these seven worlds was not [possible], grant me grace,</l>
<l>[Lord] who stands in Tiruveḷḷaṟai where the bees hum sweet melodies,</l>
<l>As in the midst of the forest of enduring screw pine and mango trees,</l>
<l rend="indent">swarms of drones whirr.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
